e.s3.amazonaws.com/Bitmap.png"> <p>JJC USA</p></img> </div> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> <table class="inner"> <tr> <td> <table> <tr> <td width="100%"> <table style="Margin:0 auto;" width="90%"cellpadding="25" cellspacing="0"> <tr style="background-color:#ffffff;"> <td style="padding-left:20px;padding-right:10px;text-align:left"> <p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px; margin-top:0;padding:0;margin-bottom:25px;"> Jai Jinendra <span th:text="${firstName}"></span>! </p> <p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px; margin-top:0;padding:0;margin-bottom:25px;"> Welcome to Jain Jagruti Centre, USA (JJC SA USA). Your Profile has been approved by our Admin! </p> <p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;padding:0;margin-bottom:25px;"> <p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;padding:0;margin-bottom:25px;"> We are a growing organization of 1200+ Jain students and working professionals in the US. We are building a platform with the primary purpose of helping Jain students and working professionals in the United States with the aim to provide:</p> <span style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px; margin-top:0;padding:0;">These include,</span> <ul style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px; margin-top:0;margin-bottom:25px;"> <li>Opportunities for networking</li> <li>Support individuals’ professional & career growth</li> <li> Assist them in building a strong community</li> </ul> <p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px;padding:0;margin-bottom:25px;">We have 5 pillars that function together to support our member community.</p> <span style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px; margin-top:0;padding:0;">They are,</span> <ul style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px; margin-top:0;margin-bottom:25px;"> <li>Alumni Welfare Committee</li> <li>Student Welfare Committee</li> <li> Social Events Committee</li> <li>Website Development</li> <li>Marketing and Communication</li> </ul> <p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px; margin-top:0;padding:0;margin-bottom:25px;"> To stay connected and interact with our members, you can join the JJC SA USA Telegram Group and Whatsapp Regional Groups. To be added in these groups you can text us on our WhatsApp number. You can find us on these channels. </p> <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" class="border-complete deviceWidth"> <tr> <td align="center" valign="top" id="socials"> <table id="social-icons" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"> <tr> <td> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/jjcusa/"><img style="padding-left: 10px; display:block;" src="https://jjc-email-template.s3.amazonaws.com/image+3.png" width="32" height="32" /></a> </td> <td> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCERP8n9IzMXT6eqZtUQVovw?view_as=subscriber"><img style="padding-left: 10px;display:block;" src="https://jjc-email-template.s3.amazonaws.com/image+5.png" width="32" height="32" /></a> </td> <td> <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jjc-us-student-association/"><img style="padding-left: 10px; display:block;" src="https://jjc-email-template.s3.amazonaws.com/image+6.png" width="32" height="32" /></a> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> <p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px; margin-top:0;padding-top:20px;;margin-bottom:25px;"> Wish to volunteer? Need assistance? Have questions? You can reach out to us by sending an email at <span style="color: #244f90 !important;text-decoration: none;">jjcsausa@gmail.com</span> or Whatsapp. </p> <p style="color:#4a4a4a;line-height:19px; margin-top:0;padding:0;margin-bottom:25px;"> Again, we welcome you to this organization and if you have any questions please do not hesitate to reach out to us. </p> <img style="width: 100%" data-imagetype="External" src="https://jjc-email-template.s3.amazonaws.com/image+7.png"> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> <table> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </table> </div> </section> </body></html>'
